1. Trust & Human Layer (New Core Web3 Category)
The missing layer of Web3.
As AI agents, bots, and sybil attacks scale faster than human participation, Web3 requires a dedicated layer to verify real humans, establish reputation, and align incentives across ecosystems.
The Trust & Human Layer serves as the foundation for human-first, sybil-resistant Web3 systems.

